column5:
21 pages, 9 figures; accepted for publication in Phys.Rev.D;
  revisions to Section IV. A and Appendix A, as well as other minor changes
  from submitted version

column11:
  We show the equivalence of the classical Helmoltz equation and the fractional
Helmholtz equation with arbitrary order. This improves a recent result of Guan,
Murugan and Wei \cite{gmw2022}
